{"tid":2431942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線 9911赤子誠可以盈喜後又出盈警既咩？","createTime":"2021-03-04T03:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:51:14.000Z","uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5deff2acc96f2912cf74dceff24e7b29fa20af1d","tid":2431942,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"赤子城過去一周升幅火爆，月初至今從2.76元升至最新7.5元以上，累計升幅達約1.8倍。不過，快手股價今早曾跌穿300元，收報303元，升1%，成交額85億元。<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">赤子城此前發盈喜</span></span>，預期去年將錄得總收入約10.5億至13.5億元人民幣，按年增長150%至250%。赤子城表示，收入增長主要是由於社交業務的快速發展，包括用戶規模的增長、市場覆蓋的擴大、變現形式的多元化。<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">2021-02-08</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">《公司盈警》赤子城科技(09911)料去年度純利跌30-50%</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">2021年3月3日週三 </span></span><br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 赤子城科技(09911)發盈警，預期截至2020年12月31日止年度的公司擁有人應佔利潤約3300至4700萬元人民幣(下同)，較2019年同期減少約30%至50%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證監瞓著左？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7e906f20fd8a6d51df981e7debf43aec4ef4b4","tid":2431942,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"聽日再盈喜都仲得"}]}